    "Let b ∶= max t |B (t) | denote the maximum batch size, then TracIn's time complexity is O(bpT).",
    "In the worst case where",
    "Recall that, by definition, |T| ≤ T meaning TracInCP is asymptotically faster than Tra- cIn.",
    "However, this is misleading.",
    "In practice, TracInCP is generally slower than TracIn as Pruthi et al. note."
